The paper discusses secure data outsourcing and partitioned computing, which are topics related to computer security (cs.CR), distributed computing (cs.DC), and databases (cs.DB). The paper also mentions the use of trusted servers, which falls under software engineering (cs.SE), and the need to prevent information leakage, which is a concern in cybersecurity (cs.CY).
